  "subject": "Fix sonars in policy-gui",
  "commit_message": "Fix sonars in policy-gui\n\nFixed:\n- use \"var\"\n- unused import\n- use for-of instead of \"for\" loop\n- unnecessary boolean\n- remove variable and just return\n- throw exception, not String\n- \"new method()\" => method()\n- replaced \"var\" with \"let\" in various places, because \"let\" has block-\n  level scope, whereas \"var\" is global\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-3095\nChange-Id: I4084fa374c36f21a58a3d8a6878e5bff45e457c8\nSigned-off-by: Jim Hahn <jrh3@att.com>\n",
